==English==
===Proper noun===
'''[[Ukrainian]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Ukrainian Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for [[Ukraine]] while under the rule of the [[Soviet Union]] (1917-1991).

